{"tid":441014,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞個自助點餐機真係損人不利己","createTime":"2017-10-19T09:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T16:21:42.000Z","uid":6783,"like":348,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"93bec88f6bcd6fba17479dd94c603800029c4a6a","tid":441014,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:32:50.000Z","msg":"為左慳返人手整部咁既野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲人又唔識用 咪又係要企番兩個職員喺度教人用<br />\n整個幾部機係到就淨係開一個櫃檯 <br />\n一忙起上嚟 櫃檯條隊又長 <br />\n排自動售賣機又要比班廢中廢老阻住晒<br />\n咪仲差過以前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班廢中廢老又要貪快走去用部機買<br />\n唔識禁又阻住晒 揀完又del返揀撚完又del返 <br />\n你老母你自己部手機咩 <br />\n最後禁極都唔識買就走撚左去 <br />\n班撚屌揀完d餐都仲係到 <br />\n要人幫佢地執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係火滾撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8799c57874ed1f5b921087b3f620f9f91b9cf5ee","tid":441014,"uid":21423,"like":16,"dislike":137,"score":-121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:37:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cca7ded21543a13c7fc98499d6cd13a1df7df0d","tid":441014,"uid":62277,"like":241,"dislike":8,"score":233,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:46:09.000Z","msg":"唔好話廢中廢老啦<br />\n廢青咪又係煩<br />\n由其是情侶/兩個女仔一齊買嗰d<br />\n屌你老母,一邊禁一邊唸一邊相量慢慢揀<br />\n<br />\n應該限時一分鐘<br />\n超時部機立刻響<br />\n螢幕彈出:你的點餐時間已完,請重新排隊輪候"},{"pid":"d2a250fdbe6487a2038c0de3340159f8ced47d87","tid":441014,"uid":62277,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:50:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我晚晚都吮人不脷己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n胸太小,自己吮不到"},{"pid":"46ab1a8db33c8fddc8a608e27efa089a10c85bd8","tid":441014,"uid":71441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"幾好用"},{"pid":"ce23663980ff49922eba8e54c4915903a19dde23","tid":441014,"uid":23160,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-1